{"tid":388884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河北唐山百回民打砸收費站 逼警下跪","createTime":"2017-09-05T17:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T04:40:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1f4ddcd27790dc87e3be762c8b1719f009036c","tid":388884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZcwmUJ0YxNs?list=PLdQbbGWbBgVPq4_Rd-Jr8TbdEoYrELbQ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZcwmUJ0YxNs%3Flist%3DPLdQbbGWbBgVPq4_Rd-Jr8TbdEoYrELbQ0&d=L2dfYzRcMKmH5xMrHVq0VwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4c0e7e79\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZcwmUJ0YxNs?list=PLdQbbGWbBgVPq4_Rd-Jr8TbdEoYrELbQ0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國河北唐山日前發生一起回族群眾打砸收費站的群體性事件，當地政府發布通報，指事件因穆斯林楊振峰被收費站工作人員毆打導致。而在微博上，「唐山收費站」等詞被列為敏感詞，禁止搜索。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台報導，2日晚上，河北唐山開平窪里收費站發生一起打砸事件。根據古冶區政府報告，當天下午6時，阿訇（伊斯蘭教教職人員）楊振峰途徑開平區境內205國道東出口收費站，因故被收費站工作人員毆打。此事引起開平夏莊等區域回族不滿，大量群眾將收費站圍堵。因收費站負責人未及時到現場，現場群眾情緒越來越激動，出現破壞收費站設施的行為。<br />\n<br />\n根據現場視頻可見，在場的穆斯林群眾情緒激動，以石塊打砸手持盾牌的人士，收費站也被砸得一片狼藉。有消息指出，到場的防暴警察也被打到跪下，視頻亦傳出「跪下」的喊聲。不過也有網友稱，當時收費站排隊車輛較多，楊振峰一行三人想走封閉車道被拒，因此發生爭執、引爆衝突。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，事發後，不少參與打砸的穆斯林被抓。另有網友指，3日上午，上百名穆斯林繼續聚集衝擊開平政府。目前微博上「唐山收費站」等詞已被列為敏感詞，禁止搜索。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有傳聞指政府打算賠500萬元息事寧人，但穆斯林們另提出要求：有關人員要賠禮道歉撤職，徹底拆除收費站，把清真寺裡外翻修一遍。<br />\n<br />\n此事在網上引起熱議，有人批：「憑什麼少數民族就能有特權！」、「穆中無人，穆無法紀。」但也有人認為，唐山被砸的收費站一直有負面消息存在，「超期6年收費，還強占周圍村的集體用地建辦公樓，明擺著就是官商勾結的地痞流氓。我們漢族群眾低調不敢吭聲，回族群眾為民除害！」、「這個收費站早該砸了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7335/2683261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7335%2F2683261&d=L2dfYzRcMKmH5xMrHVq0VwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a0cdcfe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7335/2683261</a>"},{"pid":"6504897e074267a2ce2a4c82934181fffe9ea64d","tid":388884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80b0bf99f285597e5cd6c3381110bf8c4cc85e7","tid":388884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"穆斯林 VS 蝗"},{"pid":"b98d9137ae99d593af88676ace96c13cea04a197","tid":388884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cac24b1a0532e3b590a5df4f3002e2e4060654b","tid":388884,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T20:15:52.000Z","msg":"我們漢族群眾低調不敢吭聲，回族群眾為民除害！<br />\n<br />\n香港果班成長緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fac78b8ad943e3bdc019af57eab7b8870e1e8d","tid":388884,"uid":16414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>穆斯林 VS 蝗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n穆中無人，穆無法紀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad3890ead0c0feca450e4b7cd783301704ad856","tid":388884,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T00:02:53.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑"},{"pid":"d774518d2caa58d7b4654de36e32bf575e9b2731","tid":388884,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"中華民族希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee3e2197d4e36c238909c3d8419b42c3d60401a","tid":388884,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"支那人大戰蛔族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376924e343ef04e19b19178dde5290ef5a7ec34c","tid":388884,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}